==Useful Info==
'''Eyes of devastation''' are slow, floating monsters which shoot bolts of devastation, dealing irresistible damage to and [[vulnerability (status effect)|halving the will]] of anything within range. They have decent durability but no useful [[resistance]]s.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Their bolts can kill off even rather beefy mid-game characters in two or three solid hits and make quick work of fragile casters. Hit them as hard and as fast as you can.
*They are especially dangerous when hexers are around, as their bolts will make you more vulnerable to hexes.
*If you can't blast it at range, use a corner to lure it into melee range to avoid getting shot while charging in.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.31]], eyes of devastation had '''Energy Bolt''' instead of Bolt of Devastation, which did not cut willpower in half.
*Prior to [[0.20]], their Energy Bolts could destroy walls.
